==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unbecoming
<hw>Un`be*com"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>un-</ets> not + <ets>becoming</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not becoming;
unsuitable; unfit; indecorous; improper.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My grief lets <qex>unbecoming</qex> speeches fall.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un`be*com"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un`be*com"ing*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unbed</ent>⟦br⟧
